&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This is a&lt;strong&gt; 6-month W-2 contract&lt;/strong&gt; role, fully&lt;strong&gt; onsite&lt;/strong&gt; in &lt;strong&gt;Redmond, WA &lt;/strong&gt;(no remote work and no relocation assistance provided). We offer &lt;strong&gt;competitive pay, full benefits, PTO, &lt;/strong&gt;and an outstanding company culture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Be Doing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute system-level testing and validation across Windows-based PC and gaming platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
