&lt;li&gt;Validate Windows platform functionality, device drivers (including graphics/display drivers), firmware, and overall system behavior across pre-production PC devices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, reproduce, troubleshoot, and document defects with clear and detailed bug reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze logs, system behavior, and test results to support root-cause investigations.&lt;/li&gt;
