&lt;li&gt;Review test plans and contribute to test automation efforts where applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with engineering teams to improve product quality, stability, and user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;What We Need to See&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
