&lt;h1&gt;Recruiting Coordinator – Supporting Ford – Glendale, KY (Onsite)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ford is building the workforce behind one of the most consequential manufacturing buildouts in the country — next-generation EV battery production in Glendale, KY, driving U.S. energy independence and the future of American mobility. We’re hiring a Recruiting Coordinator to work onsite alongside Ford’s talent and operations teams, supporting the hiring engine that will help staff this facility at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-visibility, high-velocity role for someone who wants to do meaningful work, move fast, and grow into broader Talent Acquisition responsibilities as the site continues to scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be on the ground in Glendale, supporting high-volume hourly recruiting, candidate engagement, recruiting events, and onboarding coordination. As the organization continues to grow, this role will expand into broader recruiting coordination responsibilities, including interview scheduling, offer support, onboarding coordination, and talent operations support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is detail-oriented, thrives in a fast-paced environment, and enjoys creating an exceptional candidate experience while partnering closely with recruiters, hiring managers, and business leaders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Candidate Experience &amp;amp; Coordination&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Serve as a primary point of contact for candidates throughout the recruitment process&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conduct candidate pre-screen conversations focused on logistics, process expectations, and NDA requirements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain consistent communication to ensure a positive and professional candidate experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collect and manage candidate documentation, including NDAs and onboarding materials&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Interview Scheduling &amp;amp; Recruiting Operations&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Coordinate and schedule interviews across multiple teams and stakeholders&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage interview logistics, confirmations, and calendar coordination across time zones&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support recruiters with candidate tracking, pipeline management, and process administration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain accurate candidate records and recruiting documentation&lt;/p&gt;
